{"tid":1632302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 聽日幾點開花？做啲乜嘢好？","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:07.000Z","uid":65196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"68c10aff565f8ac1aad58456075e64fa184d2c47","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"今日大家損耗都好大<br />\n出面已經一大堆post話文宣追唔上<br />\n先唔好講有冇人分化<br />\n但係實在影響相當多抗爭者嘅心情<br />\n<br />\n其實裝修都已經三日<br />\n以荃灣、銅記為例<br />\n其實已經冇乜嘢好再裝<br />\n你爆左都要由佢整返好先再爆㗎<br />\n<br />\n聽日我提議<br />\n不如裝修式開花停一日<br />\n裝飾、文宣式十八區開花？<br />\n<br />\n1. 各區連儂牆集合<br />\n重置文宣、更新文宣<br />\n呢幾日落雨爛咗好多<br />\n<br />\n2. 各區商場集合<br />\n唱榮光、和平集和平散<br />\n遍地開花式文宣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esHO0ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesHO0ZQ.jpg&h=3f22d379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同路人覺得可以一試嘅話<br />\n就幫幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b095c7d819c66a4b846ee5b5e3b345d3cf8ed60a","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:33:51.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0cff8fddebdc4c72f10f0858fcd05e8cf9559f3f","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"df770fe8fad0dd8bfaf0b68a18915951374f3453","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"9db39e134c6797d47b76187d9affa4a3d5e777a9","tid":1632302,"uid":126515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e103e1f27fc36de28217b33b3e66f3639954cc8","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2bbf51955c0c106fa8aa1f80073467906d663c80","tid":1632302,"uid":213935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492a4b61383e4eff84abcca77e2f3a93795a632d","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"369d3b62e74cdc730dd47cce50444d720b31bab7","tid":1632302,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"ab08868691e335c388465e7719c880d8f0a3beff","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"08111c35618269644b5db2cf993ee65b07ade83e","tid":1632302,"uid":149829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:51.000Z","msg":"紅色, 就係撐共撐警大集團。<br />\n美心, 吉野家呢啲其實唔可以話佢係黑, 最多係紅, 因為佢地係言論上攻擊抹黑示威者, 呢啲舖既裝修要停, 改為裝飾算, 另外starfuck裝黎意義不大, 因為平時都係比人hea多, 留番個地方俾手足入去涼冷氣, 俾同學仔齋溫書唔幫襯會唔會仲好?<br />\n<br />\n裝修黑色目標應該係黨鐵, 福建幫優品, 富臨系列, 建制派議員既地頭<br />\n黨鐵做殺人幫兇, 建制為多年禍害香港根源, 福建幫就真係出埋人去斬手足, 所以全部一定要裝修.<br />\n<br />\n至於藍色, 就係果啲冇乜影響力既撐共撐警小店"},{"pid":"6a6d83e3a046a4552b674fb9189de5f5f53ac046","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:57.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"439da7a04dbad4a524082d474e1c5b25bef293f4","tid":1632302,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"聽日各有各做。<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<br />\n1. 唱歌 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n2. 懲罰黃店 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n3. 貼文宣 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n4. 國際戰線 (全日)<br />\n<br />\n勇武：<br />\n1. 快閃裝修爛鐵(為全民可以有得三罷) (晚上8點後)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOag9QB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOag9QB.jpg&h=a40b95bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNM8gvC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNM8gvC.jpg&h=0207aaae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e94620519c9107c459e494b2661b1a236a7a9e6","tid":1632302,"uid":100724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a0a202567923dbd8182f9e4288aae231ab97a50","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"ace94e67a799b795aaafb591df97be20941322ae","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439da7a04dbad4a524082d474e1c5b25bef293f4","tid":1632302,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"聽日各有各做。<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<br />\n1. 唱歌 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n2. 懲罰黃店 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n3. 貼文宣 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n4. 國際戰線 (全日)<br />\n<br />\n勇武：<br />\n1. 快閃裝修爛鐵(為全民可以有得三罷) (晚上8點後)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOag9QB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOag9QB.jpg&h=a40b95bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNM8gvC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNM8gvC.jpg&h=0207aaae&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"分別兩段時間會否更危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42367a4246e6c908e1e7f40fbb27add73635b456","tid":1632302,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一個準則可以破到而家死局</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5dc2a7e8d74e2e3f9e3490eb83a90600269e973b","tid":1632302,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AsuebxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsuebxZ.png&h=344e2c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗：南昌V walk／楓樹街遊樂場／長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n荃灣：沙咀道遊樂場／荃灣公園<br />\n葵芳：葵廣／林士德足球場／林金殿外<br />\n青衣：青衣城／<br />\n觀塘：apm／觀塘遊樂場／<br />\n黃大仙：黃大仙中心／黃大仙廣場／摩士公園<br />\n油尖旺：朗豪坊／麥花臣球場／<br />\n紅土黃何九：馬頭圍邨球場／亞皆老街球場／<br />\n將軍澳：黨鐵Popcorn／香港單車公園／<br />\n沙田：新城市廣場／車公廟站 曾大屋遊樂場<br />\n馬鞍山：新港城／鞍誠街花園／<br />\n大埔：大埔超級城／大埔中央廣場／<br />\n上水： 上水廣場／彩園廣場<br />\n屯門：屯門市廣場／屯門政府合署／新和里球場<br />\n天水圍：嘉湖銀座／天耀<br />\n元朗：Yoho／大馬路<br />\n銅鑼灣：紀利佐治街／東角道<br />\n太古：太古城中心／鰂魚涌公園／<br />\n柴小杏：柴灣橋／柴灣公園<br />\n西區：中山公園<br />\n南區：香港仔中心／<br />\n東涌：東薈城噴水池／富東商場"},{"pid":"dad814ae9ecd6e5d66f7710923ae84eca2da7d6c","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42367a4246e6c908e1e7f40fbb27add73635b456","tid":1632302,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一個準則可以破到而家死局</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"收返嚟做文宣"},{"pid":"cff99d5ffd88aa8c1084dff3b20db2d17455b0fa","tid":1632302,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:14.000Z","msg":"文宣全日都可以做<br />\n但勇武一定要入黑後，唔好阻人拜山<br />\n<br />\n和勇合一，不分不割"},{"pid":"3a6b602a189ef3d8716d512991f2ce08a5791247","tid":1632302,"uid":260695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbcc053a5c3741b355d7ccacb9de980162d40eac","tid":1632302,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439da7a04dbad4a524082d474e1c5b25bef293f4","tid":1632302,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"聽日各有各做。<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<br />\n1. 唱歌 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n2. 懲罰黃店 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n3. 貼文宣 (3點或更早都可以)<br />\n4. 國際戰線 (