d":293774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"無錯!!!<br />\n==============正視聽===============<br />\n絕對建議勇武可以休息一下. 再大規模裝修落去就會比個好機會去比POPO用UC去加大力度破壞, 令到國際線受到威脅.<br />\n如果美國國會過唔到人權法, 大家辛苦左幾個月既野就會白費.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}